prompt: ie. Write a short story about a moose who eats leaves
title: Short Story
response: The moose was hungry and had not eaten in days. He had tried to find food in the forest but all he found were the leaves of the trees. The leaves were not very filling and the moose was getting tired. He was about to give up when he saw a rabbit run by. The moose was hopeful and followed the rabbit. The rabbit ran into a hole in the ground and the moose was lost. The moose was about to give up when he saw a large apple tree. He climbed the tree and ate the apples that were on the tree. He was very happy and felt much better.

prompt: ie. Write an email to my boss at the bowling alley telling him I quit
title: Email
response:
